New coupon code | TPYEAR1 | Limited to first 80 redemptions | Teapulse.sg
-
What a year it has been for @Teapulse and boy have we grown! What started as a dream to bring fermented healthy drinks to the masses became a reality when we opened out first shop in Phillip Street a year ago.
-
Since then, we have had customers who turned into friends, regulars who always make us smile and countless improvements to our menu. We are definitely in the business of making healthy and tasty drinks for you.
-
To thank you for all your support thus far, especially during this #circuitbreaker period, we are offering a coupon code | TPYEAR1 | for $3 off all online purchases above $30! Happy shopping! #Teapulse
